```r
memMat <- matrix(NA,ncol=1+memMax,nrow=nrow(rawDf))
for(n in 1:nrow(rawDf) ){
  memories <- rawDf %>% 
    select(IdNoms_1:IdNoms_20) %>%
    dplyr::slice(n) %>%
    as_vector()
  
  memIndices <- memories %>%
    map(is.emptyString) %>%
    unlist()
  
  memories[memIndices] <- NA
  
  memMat[n,] <- c(rawDf$subID[n], memories)
}

memMat <- as_tibble(memMat)
```
